com.facebook.rendercore.visibility

Interface VisibilityOutput.Factory<R extends Node.LayoutResult<?>>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LithoVisibilityOutputFactory
    Enclosing class:
    VisibilityOutput

    public static interface VisibilityOutput.Factory<R extends Node.LayoutResult<?>>
    The factory that client frameworks must implement to enable VisibilityExtension to create a VisibilityOutput for every visited Node.LayoutResult during the layout pass.
